doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.10.2.js')
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js')
    script(src='javascripts/validaciones.js')
    meta(charset='UTF-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='ie=edge')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='stylesheets/icon-font-arrow.css')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='stylesheets/styles.css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Mukta+Malar:200,300,400,500,600,700,800|Noto+Serif:400,700|Roboto:100,300,400,500,700,900', rel='stylesheet')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:400,700,900', rel='stylesheet')
    script(src='javascripts/card-animation.js')
    
    script(src='javascripts/show.js')
    title Employ.me
  body
    main
      header.header
        img.logo(src='', alt='')
        .text-box
          h1.heading
            span.heading-name.u-color-white
              | Employ
              span.point-color .
              | me
            span.heading-main.u-color-white Encuentra tu trabajo ideal.
          svg.btn-arrow
            svg.information-data-icon
              use(xlink:href='images/sprite.svg#icon-angle-double-down')
      #modal1.modal.modal-edit
        h3.modal-heading
          svg.information-data-icon
            use(xlink:href='images/sprite.svg#icon-pencil ')
          |  ¡Error!
        .modal-information
          hr
          h4 No se ha podido registar, debido a que el nombre de usuario ya ha sido utilizado
        .modal-btn-container
          a#cerrar.btn-blue.btn Cerrar
      section.section-features
        h2.heading-secondary.u-color-black ¿Que ofrecemos?
        .row
          .col-1-of-3-m
            .feature-container.secondary-feature
              i.icon-font.icon-arrows-check
              h3.heading-tertiary.u-color-black Sube tu curriculum.
              p.feature-text
                | Si no tienes un currículum, te brindamos la posibilidad de crear uno y subirlo para que puedan conocer más acerca de tus habilidades. 

          .col-1-of-3-m
            .feature-container.principal-feature
              i.icon-font.icon-arrows-check
              h3.heading-tertiary.u-color-black Personal Calificado.
              p.feature-text
                | Te aseguramos que puedes encontrar a la persona ideal, calificada para lo que estás buscando como empresa. 
          .col-1-of-3-m
            .feature-container.tertiary-feature
              i.icon-font.icon-arrows-check
              h3.heading-tertiary.u-color-black Informacion Asegurada.
              p.feature-text
                | Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit facilisi, fermentum malesuada arcu praesent interdum ornare mattis eleifend, facilisis convallis rhoncus aenean urna vitae euismod.
        .row
          .col-1-of-3-m
            .feature-container.secondary-feature
              i.icon-font.icon-arrows-check
              h3.heading-tertiary.u-color-black Compatibilidad con Github®️.
              p.feature-text
                | ¡Ahora puedes dar a conocer tus proyectos más importantes de la plataforma Github®️ a las demás personas, enlaza tu cuenta y empieza!
          .col-1-of-3-m
            .feature-container.principal-feature
              i.icon-font.icon-arrows-check
              h3.heading-tertiary.u-color-black Video solicitud.
              p.feature-text
                | Haz un video presentándote y diciendo lo más interesante de ti, súbelo a YouTube®️ y enlázalo a tu cuenta, así los demás sabrán un poco más acerca de ti.
          .col-1-of-3-m
            .feature-container.tertiary-feature
              i.icon-font.icon-arrows-check
              h3.heading-tertiary.u-color-black Información en tiempo real.
              p.feature-text
                | Puedes ver la información más reciente de cada persona y con la última versión de su perfil, así puede ver si mejoraron sus experiencias o actualizaron su portafolio completo.
      section.section-start
        h2.heading-secondary.u-color-black ¿Que eres?
        .row
          .col-1-of-2-m
            .card
              .card-side.card-side--front.card-side--front-company
                h3.heading-rol.heading-tertiary Empresa
              .card-side.card-side--back.card-side--back-company
                .form-organizer
                  svg.card-exit.card-exit--company
                    use(xlink:href='images/sprite.svg#icon-close ')
                  #btn-form-1.btn.btn-form Inicia Sesion
                  #btn-form-2.btn.btn-form.btn-form-active Registrate
                  form#form1Emp.index-form.index-form-1(action='/regemp', method='post')
                    input#nombre_e.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='nombre_e', placeholder='Nombre de la Empresa', onkeypress='return soloLetras(event)')
                    input#usuario_e.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='usuario_e', placeholder='Usuario', onkeypress='return soloGit(event)')
                    input#password_e.form-input.form-input-light(type='password', name='password_e', placeholder='Contraseña', onkeypress='return soloContra(event)')
                    input#cpassword_e.form-input.form-input-light(type='password', name='cpassword_e', placeholder='Confirmar Contraseña', onkeypress='soloContra(event)')
                    input#email_e.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='email_e', placeholder='Email', onkeypress='return soloCorreo(event)')
                    // input.btn.form-btn.form-btn-light(type='button', id="submit_emp" ,value='Registrarse')
                    button#botonemp.btn.form-btn.form-btn-light(type='submit') Registrarse.
                  form#form2Emp.index-form.index-form-2(action='/loginemp', method='post')
                    input.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='usu_e', placeholder='Nombre de usuario', onkeypress='return soloGit(event)')
                    input.form-input.form-input-light(type='password', name='pass_e', placeholder='Contraseña', onkeypress='return soloContra(event)')
                    button.btn.form-btn.form-btn-light(type='submit', value='Iniciar Sesion')  
          .col-1-of-2-m
            .card
              .card-side.card-side--front.card-side--front-employee
                h3.heading-rol.heading-tertiary Aspirante
              .card-side.card-side--back.card-side--back-employee
                .form-organizer
                  svg.card-exit.card-exit--employee
                    use(xlink:href='images/sprite.svg#icon-close ')
                  a#btn-form-1A.btn.btn-form.btn-form-active Inicia Sesion
                  a#btn-form-2A.btn.btn-form Registrate
                  form#form1Asp.index-form.index-form-2(action='/regasp', method='post')
                    input#nombre.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='nombre', placeholder='Nombre', required='', onkeypress='return soloLetras(event)')
                    input#apt.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='apt', placeholder='Apellido Paterno', required='', onkeypress='return soloLetras(event)')
                    input#apm.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='apm', placeholder='Apellidos Materno', required='', onkeypress='return soloLetras(event)')
                    input#email.form-input.form-input-light(type='email', name='email', placeholder='Email', required='', onkeypress='return soloCorreo(event)')
                    input#usuario.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='usuario', placeholder='Usuario', required='', onkeypress='return soloGit(event)')
                    input#password.form-input.form-input-light(type='password', name='password', placeholder='Contraseña', required='', onkeypress='return soloContra(event)')
                    input#confpass.form-input.form-input-light(type='password', name='confpass', placeholder='Confirmar Contraseña', required='', onkeypress='return soloContra(event)')
                    input#datepicker(type='text', placeholder='Fecha de Nacimiento', required='required')
                    br
                    select#sel(name='sexo')
                      option(value='0') Seleccionar sexo.
                      option(value='Masculino') Masculino
                      option(value='Femenino') Femenino
                    br
                    br
                    // input.btn.form-btn.form-btn-light(type="button",id='submit', value="Registrarse")
                    button#botonemp.btn.form-btn.form-btn-light(type='submit') Registrarse.                
                  form#form2Asp.index-form.index-form-1(action='/loginasp', method='post')
                    input.form-input.form-input-light(type='text', name='usu', placeholder='Usuario o Correo', required='', onkeypress='return soloCorreo(event)')
                    input.form-input.form-input-light(type='password', name='contra', placeholder='Contraseña', require='', onkeypress='return soloContra(event)')
                    button.btn.form-btn.form-btn-light(type='submit') Iniciar Sesion
